Zepto Sales Analysis using SQL

Project Overview:
This project analyzes Zepto sales data using PostgreSQL to derive business insights, identify sales trends, and evaluate product performance.

Objectives:
Analyze sales performance and revenue trends.
Identify top-selling products and categories.
Evaluate customer purchasing behavior.
Generate business insights using SQL queries.

The dataset contains:
Product information
Category details
Sales transactions
Revenue and quantity sold

Tools & Technologies:
PostgreSQL
SQL
GitHub
pgAdmin

Key SQL Concepts Used:
SELECT Statements
JOINs
Aggregate Functions
GROUP BY
ORDER BY
Subqueries
Common Table Expressions (CTEs)
Window Functions

Analysis Performed:
Total Revenue Analysis
Top Selling Products
Category-wise Sales Performance
Monthly Sales Trends
Product Ranking Analysis

Project Structure:
dataset/ – Raw data files
queries/ – SQL scripts
results/ – Output screenshots
README.md – Project documentation

Key Insights:
Identified the highest revenue-generating products.
Analyzed category-wise sales contribution.
Found trends in customer purchasing patterns.
Generated actionable business recommendations.
